msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-info-circle\"/> The default target record getter will work "
"out-of-the-box for any webhook coming from another Odoo instance."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-info-circle\"/> ຕົວດຶງຂໍ້ມູນບັນທຶກເປົ້າໝາຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈະເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ທັນທີສຳລັບ "
"webhook ທີ່ມາຈາກ Odoo instance ອື່ນ."

#. module: base_automation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:base_automation.view_base_automation_form
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-warning\"/> Automation rules triggered by UI changes will "
"be executed <em>every time</em> the watched fields change, <em>whether you "
"save or not</em>."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-warning\"/> ກົດລະບຽບອັດຕະໂນມັດທີ່ຖືກກະຕຸ້ນໂດຍການປ່ຽນແປງ UI ຈະຖືກເຮັດວຽ"
"ກ <em>ທຸກໆຄັ້ງ</em> ທີ່ຟີວທີ່ກວດເບິ່ງມີການປ່ຽນແປງ, <em>ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານຈະບັນທຶກຫຼືບໍ່ກໍຕາມ</em>."

